reviews.review_text: 6-19-86 Good show. Very nice C Miller remaster. These shows are obviously matrix recordings. I'm always shocked when I'm the first to review a Miller remaster. I recently retired and started writing reviews in appreciation of the good people who took the time to review shows before me. It really helped me in deciding what to download.

matrix, no. dan's ultra-mix i believe during the 86-89ish era dan would mix a fair amount of aud mic's with the soundboard, to create a realistic sound, this was dumped for one reason or another in the 90's.

but man it sounds great
